text.#text:
{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「急にスケッチブックが欲しいなんて、ういったらどうしたのかな？<br />確かにういの周りって、不思議と特技というか才能のある子が多いけど<br />それで何かにチャレンジしようと思ったのかな…？<br />ふふっ、ういが何を描くのか、今からちょっと楽しみかも」
| en = "Suddenly wanting a sketchbook, what's up with that Ui all of a sudden? Certainly Ui's got a lot of talented kids around her that you could call mysterious or even special, so maybe she's trying to challenge herself with something because of that...? Fufu, I wonder what Ui will draw? I'm getting a little excited just thinking about it."
| na = I wonder why Ui suddenly wanted a sketchbook? There do happen to be lots of talented girls around her...I wonder if she wants to measure up to them...? Hehe, I'm looking forward to whatever she draws.
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Tamaki Iroha]].
<!-- https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/350458702463107073/353827338125049856/Screenshot_2017-09-03-12-00-48-812_com.aniplex.magireco.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| en = 
| jp = 「なんでモデルなんて続けてるんだろう…？って考えるとね、<br />私の魔法少女としての人生が、ここから始まったからだと思うの。<br />辞めてしまえば、惨めだったことも、悲しんだことも、<br />幸せだったことも、全部無くなってしまう気がするのよね」
| na = "Whenever I wonder why I keep on modeling, I remember that my life as a Magical Girl started from here. If I were to quit, why, that would render everything: all the trials and tribulations, all the miseries and joys, rather pointless." )
}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Nanami Yachiyo]].
<!-- https://i.imgur.com/38d4ngu.jpg -->

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「最強を目指す魔法少女は、どんな時でも最強を目指す！<br />もちろん、体育の授業のバスケットボールでも！<br />わたしにボールを回してくれれば、バッチリ決めちゃうから！<br />トラベリング？何それ？そんなんでわたしは止められないよ～!!」
| en = "A magical girl aiming to the strongest will aim to be the strongest anywhere, any time! Of course, that includes playing basketball during gym class, too! If you'd just pass me the ball, I'll prove it without a doubt! Traveling? What's that? Something like that isn't going to stop me~!!"
| na = If you wanna be the Mightiest Magical Girl, you need to be the best at everything! Basketball is no exception! Pass the ball to me, I'll score for sure! Traveling? What's that? Silly rules like that can't stop ME!
}}
{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Yui Tsuruno]].

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/75KZ6Al.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = お気に入りのお菓子を食べ切っちゃったのも、<br />携帯の充電がギリギリになっちゃったのも、<br />期待外れで思わずため息が出ちゃうのも、<br />全部、全部、アンタのせいじゃないから。待ってたわけじゃないから。
| en = When I've finished all of my favorite snacks, and my phone battery is about to die, and I'm so disappointed I involuntarily let out a sigh, none of it, none of it is your fault, because it's not like I was waiting for you.
| na = Eating all my favorite sweets, my phone almost running out of batteries, sighing in disappointment... These things have nothing to do with you. Not at all. It's not like I was waiting or anything.
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Minami Rena]].

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/tVBS34l.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 大好きなあの子にだって、辛いことはたくさんあるはず。<br />それでも私に、笑顔をくれる、勇気をくれる。<br />いつだってキミがいるから、私は青春のステージに立てるんだ。<br />だから全力で叫ぶんだ。キミがアイドルのステージで輝けるように。
| en = For that girl that I love, there must be many painful things for her.

Even still, you make me smile, and you give me courage.

Because you are always there, I am standing on the stage of my youth.

That's why I shout with all my might. So that you may shine upon the idol's stage.
| na = Even you, who I love so much, have bad days, for sure. Even still, you bring a smile to my face and give me courage. I can stand on my own personal stage as long as you're there. I scream with all my might, so you can shine from your idol's pedestal.
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Togame Momoko]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 美味しいお水が好き？どんなご飯が好き？口笛は好きかな？言葉は通じないけれど…あなたたちが好きなもの、私、頑張って考えてみるの。<br />だから、お友達になってくれるかな？たくさん遊んだその後で…お昼寝の夢の中では、お喋りできたら素敵だね。
| en = Do you like the delicious water? What kind of food do you like? Do you like whistling? I can't reach you with words, but... I'll try my best to figure out the things you like.

So, do you think you could become friends with me? We could play a lot, and then... while we're dreaming during an afternoon nap, it would be lovely if we could talk to each other then.
| na = Do you like this tasty water? What kind of food do you like? How about whistling? I know we can't communicate... So I'll try to figure it out myself. Will you be my friends? We could play together, then take a nap... I'd love it if we could chat in my dreams.
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Akino Kaede]].

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/S9i3OPY.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「私の朝は、まず道場の掃除をしてからの…素振り千本！これです！<br />ただーし！振り回せばいいというものではありません…。<br />神経を研ぎ澄まし、動きをひとつひとつ確認することが肝要！<br />体に染み込ませた動きこそ、実戦で活きてくるというものですよ！」
| en = "My mornings start with cleaning the dojo... then a thousand practice swings! Like this! But~! It's not a matter of just swinging your sword around... you're sharpening your senses, and checking your movements one by one is vital! When these moves have been drilled into your body, you'll be able to use them during actual combat!"
| na = Every morning I start by cleaning the dojo, and then... 1,000 practice swings! This is important! However! Don't just swing recklessly...Calm you nerves and check each and every movement! Every lunge counts in a real battle!
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Tatsuki Asuka]].

<!-- https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/350458702463107073/353829203008946176/Screenshot_2017-09-03-12-10-28-272_com.aniplex.magireco.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = ももこ「おっし、やちよさんに負けちゃいられない。<br />使い魔なんざサクッと倒して行くよ、いろはちゃん！」<br />いろは「はい、小さいキュゥべえが案内してくれるからって<br />油断は禁物ですよね。後ろからのサポ－トは任せてください！」
| en = Momoko: " 'kay, we can't let Yachiyo-san beat us!<br />Let's go slice up those familiar thingies, Iroha-chan!"<br />Iroha: "Okay, the little Kyubey is guiding us, so be on your guard. I'll support you from the rear, so leave it to me!"
| na = Momoko: "All right, we gotta beat Yachiyo. Let's quickly take care of these Minions, Iroha!"<br /> Iroha: "Right! The small Kyubey is leading us, but that doesn't mean we can lower our guard! I'll support from behind!"
}}

{{SimilarEffects|}}
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
{{MemoriaTrivia|}}
*This memoria features [[Togame Momoko]] and [[Tamaki Iroha]].

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/rxHoeuz.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 日常的に言い争いをしている彼女達でも、互いに寄せる信頼は本物。<br />戦いが始まれば喧嘩していたのが嘘だったかのように<br />息の合った連携で次々と敵を倒していく。<br />「レナは正面の敵、かえでは左右の敵を！背中はアタシに任せな！」
| en = The girls may have their everyday squabbles, but the trust they put in each other is real.<br />When a battle begins, the fights they had with each other become as if they were all a lie, and the coordinated combination takes out enemies one after another.<br />"Rena, you get the enemies in the front, and Kaede, take the enemies on the sides! Leave the ones in the back to me!"
| na = Though they may squabble, the trust between these three is sincere. When a battle begins it's as if they had never argued at all. They fight in perfect sync, defeating enemy after enemy. "Rena take that one in the middle, Kaede tackle the ones on the sides! Leave the rear to me!"
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Togame Momoko]], [[Akino Kaede]], and [[Minami Rena]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = ももこ「レナ、かえで、準備はできてるか？」<br />かえで「う、うん…」<br />レナ「はぁ…、アンタ誰に向かって言ってんのよ。当たり前でしょ」<br />ももこ「おっし、それじゃぁ…魔女狩りといきますか！」
| en = Momoko: "Rena, Kaede, are you ready to go?"<br />Kaede: "Y-yeah..."<br />Rena: "Ugh... who do you think you're talking to? Of course I'm ready."<br />Momoko: "All right, then... shall we go witch hunting?!"
| na = Momoko: "You ready, Rena? Kaede?"<br />Kaede:"Y...Yes..."<br />Rena:"Pfft, who do you think you're talking to? Of course I am"<br />Momoko:"All right! Time to hunt some witches!"
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Togame Momoko]], [[Akino Kaede]], and [[Minami Rena]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
<!-- https://i.imgur.com/zIzql6n.jpg -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「私は魔法少女！<br />夢と希望を叶える魔法少女！<br />でも、それって秘密のことで…。<br />だから、クラスのみんなには内緒だよ！」
| en = "I am a magical girl! A magical girl who can grant wishes and make dreams come true! But that needs to be a secret... so, please keep this a secret from everyone in class!"
| na = I'm a Magical Girl! A Magical Girl who grants wishes and makes dreams come true! But, that's secret, so... Please don't tell my classmates!
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Kaname Madoka]].

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/CuKGdVQ.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = おそろいのメガネをかけて街を歩くと<br />いつもの街並みも、レンズ越しには違う景色のように見える<br />日が暮れるまで一緒に歩いていた<br />ずっと心も近付けたまま…
| en = Walking around town wearing matching glasses, the regular view of the cityscape as seen through the lenses looks like completely different scenery. They walked together until sunset, and their hearts grew closer the whole time...
| na = Wearing matching glasses, the walk through town admiring the same old scene with a new perspective through the lenses. Hearts united, they walk until the sun sets...
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Akemi Homura]] and [[Kaname Madoka]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

<!-- Title could probably be better, bespectacled girls, https://ssl-stat.amebame.com/pub/content/8265872137/user/article/unknown/unknown/451314875376885687/5d0ee8162609f19277ff76669bcbbf48/uploaded.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 一人は、その鋭き刃をもって闇夜を切り裂き、<br />一人は、その猛き銃砲をもって悪夢を撃ち抜き、<br />一人は、その揺らめく槍をもって脅威を貫き、<br />一人は、その煌く盾をもって時を彷徨い歩き、因果を結びつけてゆく。
| en = One carries a sharp sword that slices through the darkness,<br />One carries a fierce gun that blasts away nightmares,<br />One carries a swaying lance that pierces any threats,<br />and one carries a glittering shield that makes time wander, and they are all tied by fate.
| na = One slices through night shadows with her sharp blade, one blasts through nightmares with her gun, one spears the threat with a wavering lance; one strides through time, buckler shimmering, entwining their fates all the more.
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}} 
*This memoria features [[Akemi Homura]], [[Sakura Kyouko]], [[Tomoe Mami]], and [[Miki Sayaka]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}
{{MemoriaLore
| jp = さやか「よーし、やっちゃおうかな…それーっ！」<br/>まどか「きゃっ！もう、さやかちゃん！冷たいよ～！」<br/>杏子「うわっと！やめろって！アイス溶けんだろ！」<br/>さやか「へへ～！溶けろ溶けろ～！」
| en = Sayaka: "Okay, let's do it ... that's it!" <br/>Madoka: "Kya! Sayaka-chan, it's cold!" <br/>Kyoko: "Woah! Stop it! You're melting the ice!" <br/>Sayaka "Hehe! Melty Melting!"
| na = Sayaka: "Here I come... Splash attack!" <br/> Madoka: "Eep! Hey, Sayaka! It's cooooold!" <br/> Kyoko: "Ugh, quit it! My ice cream's gonna melt!"<br/> Sayaka: "Heheh, melt away!"
}}
{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Kaname Madoka]], [[Miki Sayaka]], and [[Sakura Kyouko]].
</div>

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「どんな魔女が相手だって、私たちは負けない！<br />変えられない運命なんてない！<br />魔法少女は、夢と希望を叶えるんだから、<br />ずっと想い続ければ、奇跡はきっと起こせるはず！」
| en = "Whatever kind of witch we face, we won't lose! There's no such thing as fate that can't be changed! Since magical girls can make hopes and dreams come true, as long as you put your mind to it, you'll definitely make miracles happen!"
| na = We won't lose, no matter what Witch we take on! There's no fate we can't change! Magical Girls make hopes and dreams come true. If we keep believing, we can make miracles happen!
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Tomoe Mami]], [[Akemi Homura]], [[Kaname Madoka]], and [[Miki Sayaka]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = ふわっと広がる紅茶の香りが、彼女の体を癒してくれる。<br />魔女を倒した後の一杯の味わいは特別。<br />さっきまでの慌ただしかった戦いが嘘のように、<br />ゆっくりとした時間の流れを戻してくれる。
| en = The aroma of the black tea wafts tenderly through the air, soothing her body.<br/>The flavor of a cup after defeating a witch is exceptional.<br/>It was as if the hectic battle beforehand was a lie,<br/>As time returns to its leisurely pace.
| na ="The aroma of tea wafts through the air, soothing her body.<br/>The flavor of tea after a Witch's defeat is her favorite...<br/>Slowly bringing in peace in such a fashion, you'd never imagine she was battling mere moments before." 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Tomoe Mami]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「夢を見る度に感じていた温かい気持ち。<br />魔法少女になった理由を思い出した今なら、その理由が分かる…。<br />待っててね…どんな困難な道のりであったとしても、<br />絶対に諦めずに、私が見つけ出してみせるから」
| en = "The warmth I felt every time I dreamt.. If I think about the reason why I became a magical girl now, the reason is obvious... Wait for me... whatever difficult journey awaits me, I will never, ever give up, and I will definitely find you."
| na ="I feel warm when I dream about you. Now that I remember the reason I became a Magical Girl, I know why... Wait for me... No matter how hard it may be, I won't give up until I find you." 
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Tamaki Iroha]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「長きに渡る魔法少女としての戦いの日々。<br />数多見てきた悲しい光景…数多味わってきた辛い経験…。<br />それでも、私は生きることを決して諦めはしない。<br />過去を無意味なものにしないためにも…」
| en = "For a long time as a magical girl, my days have been filled with fighting. I've witnessed many tragic sights... have tasted many bitter experiences... Even so, I won't give up on living my life. So that the past doesn't become meaningless..."
| na ="In my many days of battle, I've seen countless sad sights, and endured just as many bitter moments... No matter what, I've resolved to live, so my past does not lose its meaning..." 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/TWV2vME.png -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Nanami Yachiyo]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「一家の命運は私の両肩にズシーンとのしかかっている…。<br />プレッシャー？もちろんあるよ！…でも私はやるんだから！<br />きっとチャンスをモノにしてみせるんだから！<br />気合はいつだって十分！この由比鶴乃に任せてっての！」
| en = "The fate of a household is weighing heavily on my shoulders...<br />Pressure? Of course there is! ...But I'm gonna do it! I'll definitely prove that I can take advantage of an opportunity!<br />Putting my spirit into it is enough! Just leave it to Yui Tsuruno!"
| na ="I'm bearing the future of my family on my own two shoulders... Under pressure? You bet! But I'll take care of it! I just gotta grab whatever chances I can, and tackle 'em with all I've got! Leave it to me, Tsuruno Yui!" 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

<!-- https://i.imgur.com/TWV2vME.png -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Yui Tsuruno]].
<!-- https://imgur.com/a/TziHh -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「私にはいーっぱい見えているよ。<br />みんなの中で輝いている、夢や希望の明かりが。<br />誰にも消させない…きっと私が灯し続けて見せるから…！<br />だって、それが魔法少女でしょ？」
| en = "I can see a whole lot of it.<br />The shining light of dreams and hope inside everyone.<br />I won't let anyone to extinguish them... I'll definitely continue to light the way, just you see...!<br />After all, isn't that what a magical girl does?"
| na =Inside every person, there's a brightness...their hopes and dreams. I see it eeeverywhere! I won't let them be snuffed out...I'll protect them, keep them burning! I mean, that's what a Magical Girl does after all! 
}}

<!-- {{SimilarMemoria|effect1 = Regenerate HP|icons1 = {{Regenerate HP}}|effect2 = Disable Restraint}}
<nowiki> </nowiki>-->
<div style="overflow: hidden;">

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Kaname Madoka]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「あの時、私は約束をした。必ずあなたを守り、そして救う、と。<br />たとえ時の大河を何度渡ることになろうとも、私は後悔なんてしない。<br />立ち塞がる敵がいるのなら、引き金を引くことも躊躇わない。<br />待っていてね、鹿目さん…私が運命を変えてみせるから…！」
| en = "At that time, I made a promise. To protect you without fail, and to save you.<br />Even if I have to cross through the river of time countless times, I won't regret it at all.<br />If there's enemies standing in my way, I won't hesitate to pull the trigger.<br />Wait for me, Kaname-san... I'm going to change fate itself...!"
| na ="I promised back then. That I would protect and save you. Even if that means I have to leap through time over and over again, I won't hesitate to pull the trigger. Wait for me, Madoka... I'll change fate for you!" 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Akemi Homura (Megane ver.)]].
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 栄養バランスや注意点が細かく書かれた手書きのレシピ。<br />その筆跡から、いろはが書いたものと思われるが本人は覚えていない。<br />調理してみるものの、果たしてこれが「誰の為」の料理なのかは、<br />あのときのいろはには、わからないのであった。
| en = A handwritten recipe with detailed annotations regarding nutritional balance.

From its calligraphy, one may think that it was written by Iroha, but she herself doesn't remember.

When trying to cook it, it was a recipe for "for someone's sake" as expected.

The Iroha from that time didn't understand the reason.
| na = A nutritionally balanced recipe written with specific instructions. Seems like Iroha's handwriting, but she doesn't recall writing it. She tries making it, but she has no idea, in that moment, who she wrote it for.
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「信じられないような出来事があっても、とっても怖い目に遭っても、<br />マミさんが前を歩いてくれるから、一歩を踏み出せる。<br />マミさんがそばにいてくれるから、心を強く持てる。<br />いつもありがとうございます、強くて優しくて大好きな先輩…」
| en = ”During all the unbelievable things that happened, and all the terrifying things, too, Mami-san is there leading the way ahead of me so that I can take a step forward. Because Mami-san is by my side, my heart grows in strength. Thank you as always, my strong, kind, and beloved senpai..."
| na = I can step forward knowing Mami will be ahead of me, no matter how unthinkable, bizarre or terrifying the situation might get. I can be brave with her by my side. Thank you for being so strong, so kind, so caring... I love you.
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Tomoe Mami]] and [[Kaname Madoka]].
</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} --><!-- https://i.imgur.com/CyZs65c.png -->
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 憂いながら、彼女が紅茶の水面に浮かべるのはどんな未来だろうか。<br />救世か終末か。絶望か希望か。角砂糖とジャムをめいっぱい入れて、彼女の憂鬱を解かすことが出来るのは唯ひとり、彼女の伴侶だけかもしれない。
| en = With sorrow, the girl wondered what kind of future would float to the surface of her black tea. Would it be salvation or destruction? Despair or hope? Putting in as many sugar cubes and spoonfuls of jam as she could, the girl thought that maybe the only thing that may be able to lighten her depression was her companion.
| na = What future will rise to the surface of her teacup? Salvation or ruin? Hope or despair? Her partner alone may lift her malaise by loading her cup with jam and sugar cubes.
}}

