{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 時間は大きな川の流れのように、過去から未来へ進んでいく。<br />その流れに幾度も逆らって、彼女は果てしない旅を続ける。<br />かけがえのない友のために、自ら立てた誓いを果たすために<br />彼女は時の奔流に飛び込み、そして、抗い続ける。
| en = Time flows from the past to the future, like the flow of a big river.<br />Sailing against the flow many times, she keeps on the endless travel.<br />For the irreplaceable friend, and to fulfill her own vow,<br />she jumps into the torrent of time, and, continues to resist.
| na =Like a great river, time flows from the past to the future. Resisting the current countless times, she continues her endless journey. She leaps into the torrent again, motivated by both an oath to herself and her irreplaceable friend. 
}}

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
*This memoria features [[Akemi Homura (Megane ver.)]].

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「キュゥべえって、やっぱり変わってるよね…。<br />その、耳から伸びているのは…髪？…ひょっとしたら…手？<br />その輪っか、付いてるの？浮いてるの？<br />あと、その尻尾！…ちょっと握ってみたいかも…」
| en = "Kyuubey really is weird, don't you think? Those things growing out of his ears... hair? Or could they possibly be... hands? And those hoops, are they attached? Or floating? And then that tail! ...I kinda wanna try grabbing it..."
| na = Kyubey, you sure are strange... That thing coming out of your ear... Is that... a lock of hair or another...arm...? Those rings... are they attached to you or just floating there? And your tail!...Oh, I just want to grab it...
}}

