| en = Kyoko: "Heyyy, Sayaka! Let me have a little bite!"<br />Sayaka: "Ehh? Again? Your bites aren't just bites though..."<br />Mami: "Oh, you two, this is good! I should take a picture!"<br />Sayaka and Kyoko: "Huh?"
| na = Kyoko: "Hey, Sayaka! Gimme a bite of that!"<br />Sayaka: "What!? Another one!? Kyoko, do you even know what 'a bite' means?"<br /> Mami: "Oh, this will make the perfect picture! Say cheese!"<br /> Sayaka and Kyoko: "Huh?"
}}

