{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 妙な笑い声が聞こえてきたなら、それがサイン。<br />光る液体、カラフルな煙…爆発だって何でもござれ。きっと、もう直、最高にエキサイティングなショーの幕が上がるだろう。
| en = If you've heard a strange laugh, that's a sign. Sparkling liquid, colorful smoke... be ready for anything. Surely, a moment later, the curtain will rise on the most exciting show you might have ever seen.
| na = Your first hint is a curious giggle. Then come glowing liquids, colorful smoke and maybe even a explosion or two. It's the curtain call for the world's most exciting show!
}}

