| en = After badminton club is student council work!<br />... but before that, a brief break.<br />And there's still more of Minagi Sarara's after-school activities.<br />She still has magical girl duties, after all.
| na = Student council calls after badminton club is over! But first... A little break. Sasara Minagi has a lot of things to do after school. Not to mention her Magical Girl missions!
}}

