{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「学校も家もこの町も、上手く言えないけど、どこかしっくりこない。<br />誰かと接しても、どこを歩いても、自分の周りに薄い皮膜のようなもの<br />があって、馴染み切れない…。あの人もこんな気持ちで、自分の居場所<br />を探していたのかな。私も見つけないと…いつか、きっと…」
| en = "I can't say it well, but neither this school, this house, or this city are the same. 

Even if I meet someone, and no matter where I walk to, there's something like a fog surrounding me, and it all feels unfamiliar. I wonder if that person was looking for me, with this same feeling. If I don't find it...then someday, surely..."
| na = Nothing feels right, not at my house, my school, the town... No matter where I walk, who I talk with, I feel like I'm shrouded in a thin film keeping me from fitting into the rest of the world... I wonder if he felt the same way, trying to find a world where he belongs. I too must find where I belong, someday...
}}

