{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「困っている人たちを助けたり、空手の稽古や魔女との戦いetc…<br />結構ハードな毎日だけど、部屋に戻ってきたら…ボクの時間！<br />可愛いぬいぐるみや人形に囲まれて、少女漫画や恋愛小説を読むんだ。<br />録画したドラマも観なきゃ！あのふたり、付き合っちゃうのかなぁ～!?」
| en = 
| na = "Between helping the needy, karate practice and Witch hunts... Everyday life can kick my butt kinda hard! But back in my room it's my time. I can read girly manga or romance novels with my stuffed animal and dolls. I gotta watch the new episode of the drama I recorded too! Will those two get together this time...?!" )
}}

