{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 「たくさんの本と、目の前にはお茶とお菓子。<br />私にとっての最高の空間。<br />ページをめくる手もゆっくり動いちゃう。<br />だって、この時間をじっくりと楽しみたいから…！」
| en = "Spread out before me are a bunch of books and some tea and snacks. To me, this is the absolute best spot. I take my time turning the pages. Because I want to make sure that I enjoy this time...!"
| na = Paradise in my eyes is when books lie in heaped piles around me, tea and snacks within sight. I turn the pages gradually, not wanting to rush this lovely moment...!
}}

