{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 昼下がり、穏やかな午後。<br />みんなの前では強気でいても母の前ではやっぱり子供。<br />いつまでもこうしていられないのは彼女も分かってる。<br />でも、今だけはもう少し、夢の中に…。
| en = A calm early afternoon.<br />Even though she is strong in front of everyone, in front of her mother she is still a child.<br />She knows that it can't be like this forever.<br />But, just for now, she'll stay in dreamland a little while longer...
| na = A calm afternoon, just after midday. No matter how bossy she is in public, with her mother she's just a child. She knows she can't stay like this forever, but for now, let her dream a little.
}}

