[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 香り？色？形？―それだけじゃない。<br />贈り主の気持ちも一緒にリボンでラッピング。<br />そんな思いの詰まったブーケをあなたへ。
| en = The fragance? The color? The shape? ―That's not all. The giver's feelings are also wrapped up in that ribbon. Such a bouquet packed with those thoughts is for you.
| na = The aroma, the colors, the shape- No, not just that. She picks just the right ribbons and wraps the sender's feelings inside. Here, take the feelings and the bouquet.
}}

