| en = <b><font color="blue">Yachiyo</font></b>: "If you keep using that innertube, you'll never be able to swim, you know?"<br /><b><font color="pink">Iroha</font></b>: "Y-Yachiyo-san, don't pull on it! It's fine if I can't swim!"<br><b><font color="orange">Tsuruno</font></b>: "Yachiyo! Iroha-chan!"<br><b><font color="blue">Yachiyo</font></b>: "Eh?"<br><b><font color="pink">Iroha</font></b>: "Hm?"<br><i>Snap!</i><br><b><font color="orange">Tsuruno</font></b>: "And Yui Tsuruno got herself a couple's shot!"
