{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 温かい日射しが、少女をまどろみから深い眠りへと誘ってゆく。<br />その身の影に、自身の闇を隠した少女は、どんな夢を見るのか…。<br />「さ、環さん手伝って！」「え？え？」「こういう図太い子はね、<br />こうやって起こすのっ！」「わひゃっっははは！くすぐんなよ！」
| en = The warm rays of the sun beckon the girl from a mere slumber towards a deeper sleep. What kind of dreams is this girl, who has hidden darkness deep in the shadows of her being, having...? "Now, Tamaki-san, help me out!" "Huh? Huh?" "For cheeky girls like this, this is how you wake them up!" "Wahyaaaahahaha! Stop tickling me!"
| na = Her light nap was drawn down into a deep slumber by the warm rays of sunlight. She keeps her darkness hidden in her own shadow. What kind of dreams does she have? "Hey, Iroha, help me out!" "What? Huh?" "This is how you wake up a naughty girl like her!" "AHAHAHAHA! Don't tickle me!"
}}

