{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 叶えたい願いごとは、すぐには決められないけれど<br />人助けのために頑張る先輩の姿は、とても素敵で<br />私もあんな風に誰かの役に立てたら…と思ってしまう<br />いつしか彼女にとって【魔法少女】という存在は、憧れになっていた
| en = While she can't decide the wish that she wants to have granted right away, when she looks at her senpai who tries so hard to help people, her senpai seems so lovely that she can't help but think that she wants to be able to be useful to someone like that, too...<br />Before she realized it, she was admiring the idea of "magical girls".
| na = I still can't settle on what wish I want granted... It would be great to become a glorious hero, helping others just like Mami... Before she knew it, being a Magical Girl had become a dream for Madoka
}}

