{{MemoriaTrivia}}
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 命をかけて人を守る。<br />彼女はそんな父の背中を小さな頃から見続けてきた。<br />父は本で読んだ"騎士"の様で、憧れの存在だった。<br />憧れは夢へと変わり、父の様になりたいと思うようになる。
| en = Protecting those who put their lives on the line. That's the type of father that the girl has looked up to since she was young. Due to the book called "The Knight" that her father read to her, he became an admired figure. When her admiration turned into a dream, she decided she wanted to become like her father.
| na = As a child, she watched her father as he put his life on the line to save others. He looked like a brave knight in a picture book. That admiration transformed into a desire to be just like him. 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

<!-- https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/350458702463107073/357605005781630977/Screenshot_2017-09-13-22-13-50-214_com.aniplex.magireco.png -->
