[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| en = One of the spirit and knowledge of the tea ceremony, "Treasure every meeting, for it will never recur."<br />Meeting people may be once in a lifetime.<br />That is why you do your hospitality with all your mental faith.
| jp = 茶道の精神と心得の1つ“一期一会”。<br />人との出会いは一生に一度かもしれない。<br />だからこそ、誠心誠意を尽くして、おもてなしをするのだ。
| na = In Japanese tea ceremony, there is a useful idiom: Ichigo Ichie. It means that you may meet someone only one time in your life. This is why we do our best to deliver the finest hospitality. 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 神浜の奇妙な“噂”。<br />水徳商店街に存在する謎の机と椅子。<br />そこに現れる女の子は、どんな悩みでも解決してくれるらしい。<br />迷える子羊は、その女の子を求めて今日も足を運ぶのであった。
| en = Strange “rumors” in Kamihama.<br />A mysterious desk and chair in Suzu Shōtengai.<br />A girl appearing there seems to solve any troubles.<br />The stray lamb got on its feet today in order to search for the girl.
| na = There is a strange rumor in Kamihama. There is a girl at a mysterious counseling room in the Suitoku Shopping Mall who can solve any problem you bring to her. Everyday, some lost lamb visits her there. 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
