{{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 日当たりが良く、客層も幅広い昔ながらの喫茶店。<br />そこでお手伝いをしている女の子は、<br />とても落ち着いていて、お店の雰囲気とも合っている。<br />そんな彼女だが、どこか寂しそうな顔をすることも、しばしば見られる。
| en = An old fashioned coffee shop on a sunny day with a wide range of customers.
The girl working there is calm and well suited to the shop's atmosphere.
However, that girl often looks quite lonely.
| na = There is a girl who helps out at an old fashioned coffee shop where the sun lights up the room and the young and old alike gather. With her calm aura, she fits the atmosphere well, but if you watch her closely, you might notice her making a melancholy expression...
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->

{{MemoriaTrivia}}
* Alternate translation considered: "The Other Side of Brilliance"
** This one was chosen to make reference to the other side of Hozumi Shizuku's life as a magical girl, mainly as a daughter of a cafe owner.
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| en = "Reaching out to those in need" is the significance of the existence of Takeshi "She has been taught since childhood so she has put the power to accomplish that It is the proof that it is tightening the young black belt .
| jp = 「困っている人に手を差し伸べることこそ武の存在意義」<br />幼い頃から、そう教わってきた彼女は、<br />それを成し遂げるだけの力をつけてきた。<br />若くして黒帯を締めていることこそが、その証明である。
| na = She was taught from childhood that the power of martial arts is "for giving an helping hand to those who need it". She was raised to gain strength from these principles, and that's why she can sport her black belt at this young age.
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
<!-- https://i.imgur.com/NCO0Mci.jpg -->
{{MemoriaTrivia}}
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = 彼女の家は歴史ある洋食店で、味はピカイチである。<br />お弁当になっても味のクオリティは変わらず、リピーターも多い。<br />数量限定が故、買えなかったお客さんは、<br />後日再挑戦しようと、闘志を燃やすのであった。
| en = Her house is a historic Western restaurant, and the quality of taste doesn't change even if it is a bento, and there are a lot of repeat customers. Customers who couldn't buy because of the limited quantity burned with fighting spirit to try again at a later date.
| na = Her family runs a traditional restaurant that serves up an array of taste sensations. The quality isn't diminished when packed into a bento box, hence the high volume of repeat customers. Customers who can't manage to secure one of the limited boxes come back and try again another day. 
}}

</div> <!-- MUST NOT BE REMOVED, start of div is in template called by {{ {{PAGENAME}} |Stats}} -->
<!-- https://i.imgur.com/4mVUQio.jpg -->
{{MemoriaTrivia}}
[[Category:Memoria]]

{{{{PAGENAME}} |Stats}}

{{MemoriaLore
| jp = “夏目書房”に住む彼女は、本が大好き。<br />蔵書や図書館に赴いては、時間も忘れて読書に耽る<br />本に囲まれた生活は、彼女にとっては楽園である。
| en = She lives in "Natsume Bookshop", and loves books.<br />When going to a personal collection or a library, she forgets the time and indulges in reading.<br />The life surrounded by books is a paradise for her.
| na = She loves reading and resides in "Natsume Books". Whenever she is at home or the library, she buries herself in words and loses all track of time. A life spent in the company of books is her personal paradise.
