{{MemoriaLore
| jp = あたしの願いなんてちっぽけなもんだよ。良かれと思ったのに、<br />結局は失敗しちまったんだ…。だからこそ、あたしは心に決めた。<br />今度は失敗しない、自分のためだけに生きるって。<br />これがあたしのさ、曲げられない信念なんだよ。
| en = My wish was very small. I thought I had good intentions, but it ended up being a mistake... so that's why I promised myself. Now I won't make any mistakes, and I'll live solely for myself. That's my unwavering belief, it's who I am.
| na ="My wish was such a petty, little thing. I thought it was a good one, but in the end it was a big mistake... Which is why I promised myself, from now on, no more mistakes. I'm just gonna live for myself. That's my conviction, I won't falter in it." 
}}

